Figure 1 presents the schematics of the proposed piezoresistive microcantilever designs as seen from above. The piezoresistor element layout is indicated in black. The basic model without the rectangular hole, i.e. Model#0, is also presented for a comparison. The geometric modifications in forms of introducing a rectangular hole, changing the piezoresistor length and changing the cantilever width are shown in the figure. Model#1 has three holes, Model#2 has five and Model#3 has seven identical holes. The width of piezoresistor leg is constant. The maximum tip deflection (z
